Database:
- A user has 1..* device
- A device has 1 user (owner)
- A device has 0..* notifications (that have been received)
- A notification_template has 1 admin (creator)
- A notification_template has 0..* notification (that have been sent)
- A notification has 1 notification_template (the content)
- A notification has 1 device (receiver)

